                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-550" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS THURLOW.</persName>
                  </hi>On the evening in question I was passing through Finsbury-square—I saw the prisoner running fast, I ran and caught him—he said, "What do you want? " and the officer came up and took him.</p>
